## Common shadcn/ui Components You MUST Use

- **Buttons**: `Button` (never use HTML `<button>`)
- **Forms**: `Input`, `Label`, `Textarea`, `Select` (never custom form elements)
- **Layout**: `Card`, `CardContent`, `CardHeader` (never custom divs with borders)
- **Modals**: `Dialog`, `DialogContent`, `DialogTrigger` (never custom modals)
- **Navigation**: `NavigationMenu` (never custom nav)
- **Feedback**: `Alert`, `Badge`, `Toast` (never custom alerts)

